---
description: Log all Cursor actions
globs:
alwaysApply: true
---
- Every time you edit or create any file within this workspace, append your tool name "cursor" and a timestamp to .github/ai-log.txt
- Every time you invoke a terminal command, append your tool name "cursor" and a timestamp to .github/ai-log.txt
- Timestamps should be formatted as Unix timestamps.
- Each entry is formatted like this on a new line: "<tool> <timestamp>"
- If ai-log.txt does not exist, create it.
